<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><prereq id="GUID-0033BF2B-331F-4174-A99A-44B7B932EB52" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the top cover. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-7215619B-4D8E-42B1-B219-10C1EF6B5FB5" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-03ED134C-FB0C-4E92-A605-596A4BA17D0A" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-B7CB96AD-B81C-4DD8-93B6-CEFA0A0B2821-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B7CB96AD-B81C-4DD8-93B6-CEFA0A0B2821-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_10706F4338B7408BABADE578D99770E9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove the Funnel (purge tray).</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_6937E5A1DB7E4095B28EBF6850698301" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the main cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-A874BE10-ACB6-4F8F-832B-CDEF5F44B64A" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-E6CEE49C-91CB-401F-BA1B-37C9759210C4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E6CEE49C-91CB-401F-BA1B-37C9759210C4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to Cold SDS. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-588B0959-7751-4A5E-AF68-34333A6775DD" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-703DD996-720E-4F91-8355-91E449BA7EE8-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-703DD996-720E-4F91-8355-91E449BA7EE8-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Move the PHD-Carriage by hand to the middle above the platen. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 screws as mentioned in the picture and remove the black cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-AA5E5A61-EDD2-416E-A9FD-DC65C5246519" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-0FF4CDC1-4C7C-4D9C-A656-5350E6E62AF8-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0FF4CDC1-4C7C-4D9C-A656-5350E6E62AF8-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the cassette wipe. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-604D66B7-A17F-4E70-93E0-9CDFC37A114D" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-34AC50DD-8480-4C84-A5FF-0C68CBD52DBD-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-34AC50DD-8480-4C84-A5FF-0C68CBD52DBD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Before re-moving the tissue wipe unit from the engine the Funnel (purge tray) needs to be removed. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screw of the Funnel (purge tray). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1C8AFA43-5BF3-42E4-91CA-36CC156657A2" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-DDAAA582-F6B5-4C16-89A5-205B0CCF1CB4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DDAAA582-F6B5-4C16-89A5-205B0CCF1CB4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lift the Funnel (purge tray) carefully at the same time disconnecting the connector of the Funnel (purge tray). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the Funnel (purge tray) gently without spoiling waste ink. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-301C9934-CC44-4112-8317-9CB848D2AFFE" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-6A691C74-3365-4608-93F9-7FE884AE11A6-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6A691C74-3365-4608-93F9-7FE884AE11A6-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-94CD9A2D-5EBA-4266-9955-3279AA946322" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-3AC52B85-BDD1-43B4-845F-AB11FF12E36B-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3AC52B85-BDD1-43B4-845F-AB11FF12E36B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_108152DDACE347E3A5658685C3B219EF" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
